{"desi_lesson":{"title":"Shopping Basics","target_language":"Kannada","theme":"Shopping Basics","vocabulary":[{"english":"hello","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ಕಾರ","transliteration":"namaskaara","pronunciation":"nuh-muh-ska-rah"},{"english":"thank you","target_language_script":"ಧನ್ಯವಾದಗಳು","transliteration":"dhanyavaadalu","pronunciation":"dhan-yah-vah-dah-galu"},{"english":"excuse me","target_language_script":"ಕ್ಷಮಿಸಿ","transliteration":"kshamisi","pronunciation":"ksha-mi-see"},{"english":"how much?","target_language_script":"ಎಷ್ಟು ಬೆಲೆ?","transliteration":"eshtu bele?","pronunciation":"esh-too be-lay?"},{"english":"this","target_language_script":"ಇದು","transliteration":"idu","pronunciation":"ee-doo"},{"english":"that","target_language_script":"ಅದು","transliteration":"adu","pronunciation":"ah-doo"},{"english":"one","target_language_script":"ಒಂದು","transliteration":"ondu","pronunciation":"on-doo"},{"english":"two","target_language_script":"ಎರಡು","transliteration":"eradu","pronunciation":"eh-rah-doo"},{"english":"please","target_language_script":"ದಯವಿಟ್ಟು","transliteration":"dayavittu","pronunciation":"day-ah-vit-too"},{"english":"shop","target_language_script":"ಅಂಗಡಿ","transliteration":"angadi","pronunciation":"ang-gah-dee"}],"example_sentences":[{"english":"Hello, how much is this?","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ಕಾರ, ಇದು ಎಷ್ಟು ಬೆಲೆ?","transliteration":"namaskaara, idu eshtu bele?","pronunciation":"nuh-muh-ska-rah, ee-doo esh-too be-lay?"},{"english":"Excuse me, please.","target_language_script":"ಕ್ಷಮಿಸಿ, ದಯವಿಟ್ಟು.","transliteration":"kshamisi, dayavittu.","pronunciation":"ksha-mi-see, day-ah-vit-too."},{"english":"I want two of these.","target_language_script":"ನನಗೆ ಎರಡು ಇವು ಬೇಕು.","transliteration":"nange eradu ivu beku.","pronunciation":"nan-gay eh-rah-doo ee-voo bay-koo."},{"english":"Thank you for your help.","target_language_script":"ನಿಮ್ಮ ಸಹಾಯಕ್ಕೆ ಧನ್ಯವಾದಗಳು.","transliteration":"nimma sahaayakke dhanyavaadalu.","pronunciation":"nim-mah sah-hay-ak-kay dhan-yah